<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>ICE Reporter - Emergency Alert System</title>
    <style>
      body {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2d1b1b 100%);
          font-family: 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          color: #ffffff;
          min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .emergency-header {
          background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626 0%, #ea580c 100%);
          padding: 1rem;
          text-align: center;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5);
          border-bottom: 3px solid #fbbf24;
      }
      .alert-title {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
          font-weight: 900;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.1em;
          margin: 0;
          text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
      }
      .alert-subtitle {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
          margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
          opacity: 0.95;
      }
      .main-container {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
          gap: 2rem;
          padding: 2rem;
          max-width: 1400px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);
      }
      .map-section {
          background: #262626;
          border-radius: 12px;
          border: 2px solid #dc2626;
          position: relative;
          box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      }
      .map-placeholder {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          background: linear-gradient(45deg, #374151 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, #374151 75%, #374151),
                      linear-gradient(45deg, #374151 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, #374151 75%, #374151);
          background-size: 20px 20px;
          background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          border-radius: 10px;
          position: relative;
          min-height: 500px;
      }
      .map-overlay {
          position: absolute;
          top: 50%;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
          text-align: center;
          background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
          padding: 2rem;
          border-radius: 8px;
          border: 2px solid #dc2626;
      }
      .report-pins {
          position: absolute;
          width: 20px;
          height: 20px;
          background: #dc2626;
          border-radius: 50%;
          border: 3px solid #fbbf24;
          animation: pulse 2s infinite;
      }
      .pin-1 { top: 30%; left: 40%; }
      .pin-2 { top: 60%; left: 70%; }
      .pin-3 { top: 45%; left: 25%; }
      @keyframes pulse {
          0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.7); }
          70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0); }
          100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0); }
      }
      .reporting-panel {
          background: #262626;
          border-radius: 12px;
          border: 2px solid #dc2626;
          padding: 2rem;
          box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      }
      .panel-title {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
          font-weight: 900;
          color: #fbbf24;
          margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }
      .report-type {
          background: #374151;
          border: 2px solid #6b7280;
          border-radius: 8px;
          padding: 1rem;
          margin: 0.5rem 0;
          cursor: pointer;
          transition: all 0.2s;
          color: #ffffff;
          font-weight: bold;
      }
      .report-type:hover {
          background: #dc2626;
          border-color: #fbbf24;
          transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .emergency-button {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
          border: 3px solid #fbbf24;
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 1rem 2rem;
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          font-weight: 900;
          color: #ffffff;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.1em;
          cursor: pointer;
          width: 100%;
          margin: 1rem 0;
          transition: all 0.2s;
          text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
          box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4);
      }
      .emergency-button:hover {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b91c1c 0%, #991b1b 100%);
          transform: translateY(-3px);
          box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.6);
      }
      .recent-reports {
          margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      .report-item {
          background: #1f2937;
          border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
          padding: 1rem;
          margin: 0.5rem 0;
          border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      }
      .report-time {
          color: #fbbf24;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .report-type-badge {
          background: #dc2626;
          color: #ffffff;
          padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
          border-radius: 4px;
          font-size: 0.8rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin: 0.5rem 0;
          display: inline-block;
      }
      .warning-banner {
          background: #fbbf24;
          color: #000000;
          padding: 0.5rem;
          text-align: center;
          font-weight: bold;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .main-container {
              grid-template-columns: 1fr;
              padding: 1rem;
          }
          .alert-title {
              font-size: 1.8rem;
          }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="warning-banner">
      ⚠️ ANONYMOUS REPORTING SYSTEM - YOUR SAFETY IS PRIORITY ⚠️
    </div>

    <header class="emergency-header">
      <h1 class="alert-title">🚨 ICE Reporter 🚨</h1>
      <p class="alert-subtitle">Real-Time Immigration Enforcement Alert System</p>
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
      <div class="map-section">
        <div class="map-placeholder">
          <div class="report-pins pin-1"></div>
          <div class="report-pins pin-2"></div>
          <div class="report-pins pin-3"></div>
          <div class="map-overlay">
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #fbbf24;">LIVE ACTIVITY MAP</h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
              Interactive map will show real-time ICE activity reports
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.8;">
              Red pins indicate recent reports
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reporting-panel">
        <h2 class="panel-title">🚨 Report Activity</h2>

        <div class="report-type">
          <strong>🛑 CHECKPOINT</strong> <br />
          <small>Border patrol or ICE checkpoint spotted</small>
        </div>

        <div class="report-type">
          <strong>🏠 RAID</strong> <br />
          <small>Immigration raid in progress</small>
        </div>

        <div class="report-type">
          <strong>👮 PATROL</strong> <br />
          <small>Increased ICE patrol activity</small>
        </div>

        <div class="report-type">
          <strong>🏢 DETENTION</strong> <br />
          <small>Detention center activity</small>
        </div>

        <button class="emergency-button">
          📍 SUBMIT REPORT
        </button>

        <div class="recent-reports">
          <h3 style="color: #fbbf24; margin: 0 0 1rem 0;">Recent Reports</h3>

          <div class="report-item">
            <div class="report-time">⏰ 12 minutes ago</div>
            <div class="report-type-badge">CHECKPOINT</div>
            <div>I-95 Exit 42, heavy activity</div>
          </div>

          <div class="report-item">
            <div class="report-time">⏰ 28 minutes ago</div>
            <div class="report-type-badge">PATROL</div>
            <div>Downtown area, multiple vehicles</div>
          </div>

          <div class="report-item">
            <div class="report-time">⏰ 1 hour ago</div>
            <div class="report-type-badge">RAID</div>
            <div>Residential area, avoid Main St</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
